OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775304668
OL,3,CNetwork rail upgrade could cause
OL,4,Ctravel disruption over Easter
OL,6,FDelays are expected with significant
OL,7,Fupgrades planned between Preston and
OL,8,FCarlisle.
OL,10,FThe Easter works form part of a larger
OL,11,F#400 million project to upgrade the
OL,12,FWest Coast Main Line, which Network
OL,13,FRail says is Europe's busiest mixed-
OL,14,Fuse railway.
OL,16,FAvanti West Coast will operate a
OL,17,Fspecial Preston to Carlisle train
OL,18,Fservice via the Settle and Carlisle
OL,19,Fline to keep people moving.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775304668
OL,3,CNetwork rail upgrade could cause
OL,4,Ctravel disruption over Easter
OL,6,FTransPennine Express and Northern
OL,7,Fservices will terminate earlier at
OL,8,FPreston, Oxenholme, or Grange-over-
OL,9,FSands.
OL,11,FJake Kelly from Network Rail said: "We
OL,12,Fknow how important Bank Holidays are -
OL,13,Fparticularly at Easter, when families
OL,14,Fand friends come together, and that's
OL,15,Fwhy we work hard to keep as much of
OL,16,Fthe network open as possible while
OL,17,Fcarrying out these vital upgrades.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
