OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775304668
OL,3,CNetwork rail upgrade could cause
OL,4,Ctravel disruption over Easter
OL,6,F"However, Bank Holidays are also among
OL,7,Fthe least busy times on the railway,
OL,8,Fand the four-day period at Easter
OL,9,Fgives us a valuable opportunity to
OL,10,Fcomplete projects that simply can't be
OL,11,Fdelivered during a normal weekend.
OL,12,FThis ensures we maximise the time our
OL,13,Fteams are out working on the tracks.
OL,15,F"So passengers will see some changes,
OL,16,Fand it's a good idea for people to
OL,17,Fcheck before they travel."
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@ZO]
